full_text: Desde el pragmatismo discutir sobre el uso o no de una palabra es relevante si tiene implicaciones prácticas.El lenguaje construye realidades.En el caso de la migración, palabras como: contagio, amenaza, carga y ilegal favorecen el estigma. Hay que usar otras palabras diferentes
subject: Migration
translation_deepl: From a pragmatic point of view, discussing the use or not of a word is relevant if it has practical implications; language constructs realities; in the case of migration, words such as: contagion, threat, burden and illegal favor stigma. Different words should be used
text: From a pragmatic point of view, discussing the use or not of a word is relevant if it has practical implications language constructs realities in the case of migration, words such as contagion, threat, burden and illegal favor stigma. Different words should be used

full_text: Es más, en Montreal me volvió a ocurrir, pero ahí tiene más sentido porque la comunidad era grande y ya habían pasado unos doce años desde la primera ola de migración colombiana (2001-2002). Al principio y en la ciudad de Québec sí me parecía raro porque sentía una sugerencia.
translation_deepl: Moreover, it happened to me again in Montreal, but it made more sense there because the community was large and it had already been twelve years since the first wave of Colombian migration (2001-2002). At the beginning and in Quebec City it did seem strange to me because I felt a suggestion.
text: Moreover, it happened to me again in Montreal, but it made more sense there because the community was large and it had already been twelve years since the first wave of Colombian migration (20012002). At the beginning and in Quebec City it did seem strange to me because I felt a suggestion.

full_text: Vi una pelea chimba por ahí y me hizo acordar de unas anécdotas de migrante. Cuando vivía en Québec, siempre me preguntaban si tenía novia colombiana. Me parecía muy raro, porque en el colegio de mi barrio éramos 4 migrantes y yo el único latino. La pregunta siguió siendo actual.
translation_deepl: I saw a funny fight over there and it reminded me of some anecdotes as a migrant. When I lived in Quebec, I was always asked if I had a Colombian girlfriend. It seemed very strange to me, because in my neighborhood school we were 4 migrants and I was the only Latino. The question remained current.
text: I saw a funny fight over there and it reminded me of some anecdotes as a migrant. When I lived in Quebec, I was always asked if I had a Colombian girlfriend. It seemed very strange to me, because in my neighborhood school we were 4 migrants and I was the only Latino. The question remained current.

full_text: Nos duelen los muertos que deja la violencia producto de narcotráfico y terrorismo. Entre 2010 y 2018, nuestro país vivió 189 homicidios colectivos, y entre 2019 y 2020, 34 hechos de esa naturaleza. Seguiremos combatiendo a disidencias FARC, ELN, Clan del Golfo, carteles y otros.
translation_deepl: We are pained by the deaths caused by violence resulting from drug trafficking and terrorism. Between 2010 and 2018, our country experienced 189 collective homicides, and between 2019 and 2020, 34 events of this nature. We will continue to fight FARC dissidents, ELN, Clan del Golfo, cartels and others.
text: We are pained by the deaths caused by violence resulting from drug trafficking and terrorism. full_text: ¿Cambiar los nombres ayuda más? Llaman a las masacres, homicidios colectivos; a los acuerdos de paz, paz con legalidad; a los Pedets, zonas futuro; a los desplazados, migrantes internos. Está bien; lo importante es que hoy se hagan mejor las cosas que ayer; y queda poco tiempo.
translation_deepl: Does changing the names help more? They call the massacres, collective homicides; the peace agreements, peace with legality; the Pedets, future zones; the displaced, internal migrants. All right; the important thing is to do things better today than yesterday; and there is little time left.
text: Does changing the names help more They call the massacres, collective homicides the peace agreements, peace with legality the Pedets, future zones the displaced, internal migrants. All right the important thing is to do things better today than yesterday and there is little time left.

full_text: ¡Otro descubrimiento! La migración forzada tiene efectos observables sobre el crecimiento urbano incluso después de 10 años, pero este efecto es menor cuando se dispara el desplazamiento.
translation_deepl: Another discovery! Forced migration has observable effects on urban growth even after 10 years, but this effect is smaller when displacement is triggered.
text: Another discovery Forced migration has observable effects on urban growth even after 10 years, but this effect is smaller when displacement is triggered.

full_text: ¡Hallazgo! Cuando la migración forzada es más grande, otras variables como el bono demográfico (estructura poblacional) tienen menos efecto sobre el crecimiento en las zonas urbanas de Colombia
translation_deepl: Finding! When forced migration is larger, other variables such as the demographic bonus (population structure) have less effect on growth in Colombia's urban areas.
text: Finding When forced migration is larger, other variables such as the demographic bonus (population structure) have less effect on growth in Colombias urban areas.

full_text: ¡Algo súper clave! La migración forzada ha sido determinante en el proceso de cambio territorial en Colombia. ¡Pero pilas!, este proceso no ha sido igual para todas las regiones, cada territorio cuentan una historia diferente en las que el conflicto armado transformó sus ciudades
translation_deepl: Something super key! Forced migration has been a determining factor in the process of territorial change in Colombia, but this process has not been the same for all regions, each territory tells a different story in which the armed conflict has transformed their cities.
text: Something super key Forced migration has been a determining factor in the process of territorial change in Colombia, but this process has not been the same for all regions, each territory tells a different story in which the armed conflict has transformed their cities.

full_text: ¿Qué observamos? Detectamos que la migración forzada es especialmente importante para entender el crecimiento de las ciudades colombianas durante los 90 y que en algunas áreas metropolitanas el peso de la migración forzada en los cambios urbanos es menos relevante que en otras.
translation_deepl: What do we observe? We found that forced migration is especially important for understanding the growth of Colombian cities during the 1990s and that in some metropolitan areas the weight of forced migration in urban change is less relevant than in others.
text: What do we observe We found that forced migration is especially important for understanding the growth of Colombian cities during the 1990s and that in some metropolitan areas the weight of forced migration in urban change is less relevant than in others.

full_text: ¿Qué encontramos? Que las migraciones forzadas afectan  zonas urbanas generando ampliación de dichos territorios, y que el impacto relativo de la migración forzada sobre el crecimiento de las ciudades no ha sido el mismo a lo largo del tiempo ni el mismo a lo ancho del país.
translation_deepl: What did we find? That forced migrations affect urban areas, generating the expansion of these territories, and that the relative impact of forced migration on the growth of cities has not been the same over time or across the country.
text: What did we find That forced migrations affect urban areas, generating the expansion of these territories, and that the relative impact of forced migration on the growth of cities has not been the same over time or across the country.
